{"tid":2106497,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★測試支肺Power 美國男子故意與確診者聚會 最後染疫死亡","createTime":"2020-07-13T11:19:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-13T11:46:22.000Z","uid":19454,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"28cbb9f72ebf672963d7a4f8e2d6cf54e9c45952","tid":2106497,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T11:19:52.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】美國得州一個男子參與「新冠派對」，即與確診者聚會，以試驗病毒的傳播能力，他最後染疫死亡，他臨終前承認自己犯錯，誤以為新冠疫情是惡作劇，有醫生呼籲大眾正視疫情威脅。<br />\n<br />\n美國得州聖安東尼奧一個30歲男子參加一個「新冠派對」，即是與確診者一起聚會測試病毒是否能傳染別人，或試圖做到群體免疫，結果這個男子「中招」死亡，他臨終前才知後悔莫及。<br />\n<br />\n早前有報道指，亞拉巴馬州有大學生賭誰在聚會後首先染疫，並設有獎金。有醫生批評「新冠派對」危險、不負責任和可能致命，警告即使感染後不一定等於免疫，也可以「復陽」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=397794\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D397794&d=luXbQZY1AauiUI8MFdBmxL500bRp0Z5eW4%2BYbKsxGJA%3D&h=238b1ada\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D397794&h=b6f87dbe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=397794</a>"},{"pid":"6c7b5416feda8d08c7e09676c5d17e2b5d2e6a69","tid":2106497,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T11:19:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a28185cb4b932ed69a1635e1921f3a2d2ebc6a43","tid":2106497,"uid":40997,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T11:21:25.000Z","msg":"達爾文獎大熱"},{"pid":"80d43407545d137d980d3317bf74d9584211542a","tid":2106497,"uid":16057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r